296
00:32:57,311 --> 00:32:58,251
Those are two separate.

297
00:32:58,571 --> 00:33:11,418
Those are two separate items so the substance abuse disorder is one, because we recognize that, you know, but I'm in Boston, right now and I'm in Roxbury it's a huge problem, you know, down where I am.

298
00:33:13,383 --> 00:33:14,023
So that's separate.

299
00:33:14,063 --> 00:33:14,943
That's completely separate.

300
00:33:14,963 --> 00:33:18,684
That's something that we would fund separately to the grant program.

301
00:33:18,724 --> 00:33:32,148
We anticipate the grant program would fund things like, you know, back to school backpack programs and, you know, things that support youth and other things that are needed in the Medford area.

302
